ards are popular among gamers and professionals."], "scores": [0.8014777900214627, 0.6122384331380667, 0.6068333368695011, 0.6022497951376065, 0.5980783886684115], "model_name": "bge-large", "document_ids": ["Google", "Intel", "Nvidia", "Meta", "AMD"]}}